    haec proxima verba in alio codice. [7.] Alius: _in modum_.
    [8.] Alius: _afferret_. [9.] Alibi: _lectione_. [10.] Alius:
    _amici_. [11.] Alius: _aut_. [12.] Alius: _congruum_. [13.] Alibi:
